  "logNo": "110143391809",
  "title": "체형교정 추나요법 [사당동 이수역 남성역 한의원]",
  "addDate": "2012. 7. 24.",
  "categoryNo": "14",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110143391809",
  "html_size": 192274,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110143391809\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110143391809\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">체형교정의 치료 효과</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp; </span><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">척추와 골격이 이상적인 정렬을 이룰 때 우리몸의 디스크와 관절은 정상기능을 수행할 수 있습니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">그러나&nbsp;척추가 굽어지거나, 허리와 목이 일자가 되버린&nbsp;경우, 골반이&nbsp;틀어진 경우에는 목과 허리의 디스크질환 발생위험도가 높아집니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">디스크 질환 뿐만 아니라 척추관절, 무릎관절, 어깨관절이 한쪽만 닳게 되거나 움직일 때마다 부딪혀서 소리가 나는&nbsp;증상도 발생합니다.&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered --><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WIDTH: 408px; HEIGHT: 385px; BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); CURSOR: pointer; rwidth: 408px; rheight: 385px\" id=\"20101221_37/isuhani_1292903782129L6rTk_JPEG/4_image_05.jpg\" class=\"_photoImage\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_37/isuhani_1292903782129L6rTk_JPEG/4_image_05.jpg?type=w2\" width=\"408\" height=\"386\" /></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">바른 정렬일 때에는 척추와 뼈 주변의 인대와 힘줄, 근육들이 이완된 상태로 있게 되지만, 구부정해지거나 일자가 되고 틀어지게 되면 주변의 인대와 힘줄은 약해지고 근육은 뭉치게 되죠.&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">이런 것들을 회복시켜주는게 체형교정 추나요법입니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aad53ce63cb05460.jpg\" width=\"259\" height=\"194\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 259px; rheight: 194px\" id=\"20120724_72/isuhani_1343092229399MlVG1_JPEG/images_%287%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A50EC841')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aad53ce63cb05460.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><?xml:namespace prefix = v ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" /><!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"&gt;&lt;/o:lock&gt;<!-- localfile --><!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v&gt;<?xml:namespace prefix = w ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" /><!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;w:wrap type=\"topAndBottom\"&gt;&lt;/w:wrap&gt;&lt;/v&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"&gt;&lt;/v:f&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"&gt;&lt;/o:lock&gt;<!-- localfile --><!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;v&gt;<!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered -->&lt;w:wrap type=\"topAndBottom\"&gt;&lt;/w:wrap&gt;&lt;/v&gt;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">비뚤어진 체형은 만성통증의 주된 원인이 되기 때문에 체형교정 추나요법이 필요합니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">체형이 망가지면 같은 자세를 유지하기가 힘들어지기도 하죠. 가만히 앉아있질 못하고 괜시리 불편해서 이렇게 저렇게 자세를 자꾸 바꾸게 됩니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">또한 척추와 뼈 주변의 인대와 힘줄이 약화되서 바른 자세를 유지하기 힘들어집니다. 똑바로 서거나 앉으려 해도 5분도 채 지나기 전에 구부정해집니다.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">금새 피로를 느끼게 되고, 두통, 요통, 팔다리 저림 등의 증상도 생기게 되죠. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dd00465570840981.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 160px; rheight: 240px\" id=\"20120724_185/isuhani_1343092500127UeXkH_JPEG/images_%285%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A50EC841')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dd00465570840981.jpg\"></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">자세가 나빠서 자꾸 아프게 되는 경우, 치료를 하면 잠시 괜찮았다가&nbsp;다시 아파지는 경우, 자세에 따라서 아픈정도가 달라지는 경우는 척추와 관절의 정렬이 비뚤어지진 않았는지 확인하고, 비뚤어졌으면 바로잡기 위한 체형교정 추나요법을 해주어야 합니다.&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">이수</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">한의원에서는 오랜기간의 체형교정에 대한 경험과 지식을 바탕으로 이수한의원만의 독특한 체형교정 추나요법을&nbsp; 시행합니다. </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5557f84b491177be.jpg\" width=\"317\" height=\"211\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 317px; rheight: 211px\" id=\"20120724_92/isuhani_1343092703071Pp4A2_JPEG/WO0W4531.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A50EC841')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5557f84b491177be.jpg\"></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">굳어진 척추, 관절을 풀어줍니다. </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">약해진 인대와 힘줄을 강화해줍니다. </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">뭉치고 굳어진 근육을 풀어줍니다. </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">그래서 몸의 전후좌우의 밸런스를 맞춰주어 척추,관절의 정렬을 바르게 하고 </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">만성 통증의 원인을 해결해주는겁니다. </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p></span></strong><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></strong>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">목, 허리 디스크. 어깨, 무릎 관절통. 만성적인 목, 어깨, 허리 통증. 팔 다리 저림. 만성피로. 집중력 저하. 만성두통. 여성의 자궁질환(생리통 등). 등이 체형치료의 대상이 됩니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120724_85/isuhani_1343092976528P84XU_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 193px; rheight: 48px\" id=\"20120724_85/isuhani_1343092976528P84XU_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC